msgid "Crafting"
msgstr "Artisautza"

msgid "Inventory"
msgstr "Inbentarioa"

msgid "Recipe book"
msgstr "Errezeta-liburua"

msgid "Fill Craft Grid"
msgstr "Bete Artisautza Sareta"

msgid "Crafting Table"
msgstr "Lan mahaia"

msgid "3×3 crafting grid"
msgstr "3×3 artisautza sareta"

msgid "A crafting table is a block which grants you access to a 3×3 crafting grid which allows you to perform advanced crafts."
msgstr ""
"Lan mahaia artisautzarako 3×3 sareta bat emango dizun blokea da. Horrela "
"artisautza aurreratua egiteko aukera izanik."

msgid "Rightclick the crafting table to access the 3×3 crafting grid."
msgstr "Egin eskuin-klik lan mahaian 3×3 artisautza sareta irekitzeko."
